 was not automatic.}{\plain \lang1033 
\par }{\plain \lang1033 
\par }{\plain \lang1033 A:}{\plain \lang1033 \tab }{\plain \lang1033 
It's as automatic as possible now.  Some wave drivers are just too unstable to completely rely on their reports so we ask you to manually select the sampling parameters when you first install }{\plain \lang1033 HyperMOD}{\plain \lang1033  on your system.}
{\plain \lang1033 
