\par }\pard \ri3286 
\par Use the {\ul\cf11 Sample Rate Button}{\v\f2\fs16\cf5 setup_bsr} to change the current sample rate.
\par 
\par {\ul Note}: In {\uldb\cf11 Direct Hardware Support}{\v\f2\fs16\cf5 hardware_mode}{\plain \lang1033  }mode the sample rate is locked at 44 kHz.
\par {\plain \lang1033 \page }#{\footnote \pard\plain \s245 \fs20\lang1033 # setup_bsr}{\plain \cf2\lang1033  }{\b\fs28\ul\cf2 Sample Rate Button}{\b\fs28\ul\cf2 
